                    <span>that keeps you charged about life one day at a time.  I particularly liked the layout and though some of the passages are not very long in length, they are quite large in their meaning.  Quite simply this little book can change your life no matter who you are or what you have gone through.  This little book can keep you focused and directed when you need it the most.<p>Also reccomended:  "The Power of Positive Thinking" and "The Amazing Results of Positive Thinking".</span>
                  
