                    <span>I have kept this book by my bedside for several years.  I may or may not read it every single day, but I do consider it to a 'working' bible for which each day has a message that brings hope, facilitates clarity, and  reminds one of what is truly important.  I have also bought it as a gift  for others.</span>
                  
              
